  "description": "Whether you call it a rapid ragù, a brisk bolognese or a prompt pasta, one thing's for sure, this linguine is superbly speedy! We've quickened the cooking process by not peeling the carrot (remember to wash first!) & crumbling the mushrooms right into the pan. For when you need comfort – and you need it now!",
